SUMMARY

The Inazuma Eleven protagonists as a whole, each one so far being based over their story, this its basically page to explain where they overall scale.
Powers and Stats

Tier: Varies

Key: Canon, Post Canon, Fic

Name: Mark Evans, Arion Sherwind, Sonny Wright, Destin Billows

Origin: Inazuma Eleven

Gender: Male

Age: varies, usually they are not past middle school.

Classification: Football/Soccer players.

Powers and Abilities:

Attack Potency:  Large Planet Level, characters can easily survive moves like Planet Shield, who uses quite literally a gigantic planet against the Opponent.  Star Level to Large Star Level,  multiple moves are quite literally described as Black Holes which get calculated to those level of powers without even counting the fact that moves can evolve. Multi Solar System Level, players can create Supernova which are that strong and can easily be higher via shot evolution, Move like Crossfire is stated to shakes the stars which is calculated to these levels. Galaxy level to Multi-Galaxy Level at least, Earth Eleven managed to bust a particularly big Black Hole. High Universe Level, multiple moves are described to be Infinite moves characters can literally break through with their shots. Universe Level+ players can literally do the Big Bang itself. Universe Blaster quite literally tear through space, so at the same time tear through spacetime. As the game description of Victory Road states, Football in Inazuma Eleven is Hyperdimensional which is more than 3 dimensions of space.
Low Complex Multiverse Level, as shown before in Inazuma Eleven football is more than three dimensions on it own meaning space alone is at least 4D, adding at least one of time that makes its spacetime 5D which as shown before characters can tear through.
Complex Multiverse Level, even though characters via soccer/football can affect a 5D spacetime, the move Supernova in its description to surpass the dimension of Football, making it 6D. they are comparable to Fran, who managed to create a forest that connect Inazuma cosmology with LBX cosmology merging them together, considering that place is capable of containing an at least 6D structure, it should be at least 7D, as she is also capable of destroying everything. High Hyperverse Level, the Inazuma cosmology as shown in Chrono Stone fits the interpretation for a type 3 multiverse over the universes keep branching in different other universes. As the series also under string theory, due to that if we are to go by string theory by its 11D of base, adding the other higher stuff we will reach 13-14D but since the verse has also Many World Theories, we go to at best Low Outerverse Level. Higher possibly, In canon multiple other verses exist in the IE Cosmology via crossovers and non like Professor Layton, LBX, Yo-Kai-Watch, Despicable Me, Happy Feet, and Grandpa Danger/Zettai Zetsumei: Denjarasu Jii-san, in Fic sense the series Cosmology is connected in general to Slakeverse, so DBAF, Baki, Bakugan, Ben 10 etc…Also Goonverse.


Speed: MFTL+ they have multiple calcs for this level of speed.  Immesurable due to be capable to make and react to shots that scale to the spacetime/cosmology. Higher with crossovers, Irrelevant they played a soccer match with multiple characters from Slakeverse, one of them being Baki who as his page tells transcended the concept of speed.

Range: Varies.

 

Notes: Not every characters scale to the cosmology, at least anime wise and fic wise their strength goes depending in which point of the story they are, so some are pretty fodder, others like characters from season 2 to 3 mostly scaling goes to 11D to 13-14D as explained earlier thanks to String theory, those that scale to whole cosmology both in canon and fic sense are not as many as the others.

In the Fic the scaling chain between the protagonists is this: Arion strongest, Mark second strongest, Destin is still not fully decided but he will be above Sonny at least in fic.

String theory can also go up to 26D on it alone, so going by that one can also reach 28-29D with string theory alone.

To also add, the verse is under “Multiple Spacetimes/Times theory” which have stuff like F-Theory, and fits the most Type 3 multiverse.

The team Dark Angel transcended time.
